To create local ubuntu cloud vm:

```
./ubuntu-cloud-vm.sh
```

To bootstrap the kubernetes cluster:

```
./bootstrap.sh
```

To tunnel the argocd server:

```
ssh -N -L 8080:127.0.0.1:8080 ubuntu@192.168.122.190
```

To access the argocd server:

```
http://localhost:8080
```

To access remote cluster tools:

```
kubectl --kubeconfig .kubeconfig get nodes
kubectl --kubeconfig .kubeconfig get pods -A
kubectl --kubeconfig .kubeconfig port-forward svc/argocd-server -n argocd 8080:443 --address 0.0.0.0
kubectl --kubeconfig .kubeconfig -n observability port-forward svc/kube-prometheus-stack-grafana 3000:80 --address 0.0.0.0
kubectl --kubeconfig .kubeconfig -n minio port-forward svc/minio-console 9001:9001 --address 0.0.0.0
```
